Privacy Policy for RKL Assistant
Effective Date: 4/2/2025

RKL Assistant ("we", "our", or "us") values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect the personal information of users ("you" or "your") who interact with RKL Assistant on Discord. By using the bot, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:
- User Information: When you use RKL Assistant, we may collect Discord account details such as your Discord username, user ID, and the servers you are a part of.
- Bot Commands: If you interact with the bot by issuing commands, we may log the commands you enter for troubleshooting and improvement purposes.
- Messages and Data: In some cases, the bot may read or store data from messages you send to it, depending on its functionality. This could include command data or other messages sent directly to the bot.

2. How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect for the following purposes:
- To provide and improve the services of the bot.
- To ensure the functionality of the bot by processing and responding to your commands.
- For debugging, troubleshooting, and fixing errors in the botâ€™s operations.
- To analyze usage trends to improve the bot's performance and user experience.

3. Data Retention
We will retain your information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. This may include retaining your information to improve the bot's functionality and security. You may request to have your information deleted at any time (see "Your Rights" section).

4. Data Sharing
We do not share your personal information with third parties unless:
- Required by Law: We may share information if required to do so by law or in response to legal processes (e.g., a subpoena).
- Service Providers: We may share information with third-party service providers who assist in operating the bot or providing support. These service providers are required to keep your information confidential and use it only for the purposes we specify.

5. Security
We take appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of your personal information. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

6. Your Rights
- Access: You have the right to request access to the information we hold about you.
- Correction: If you believe the information we have is incorrect or incomplete, you have the right to request corrections.
- Deletion: You may request the deletion of your data by contacting us. This may not apply to information required for legal or operational purposes.
- Opt-Out: You may stop interacting with the bot or remove the bot from your server at any time.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify users of significant changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on our website or via Discord.

8. **Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, feel free to reach out to us at:

- Email: jennywalker2704@gmail.com
